@Reasoning:
ENTRYPOINT shell-form is wrapped by /bin/sh -c at container start. It is
explicitly distinguished from CMD shell-form because Docker layers
ENTRYPOINT and CMD differently (CMD becomes positional args to
ENTRYPOINT), so the surface choice must survive the HIR round trip.
@End Reasoning

