@Reasoning:
WORKDIR is single-argument and absolutely critical: the next layer's CWD
depends on it. Empty path is permitted at HIR level because the validator
upstream may have already flagged it; the backend's job is faithful
reconstruction, not re-validation.
@End Reasoning

